  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 440333c5586acf44db3ff057db103969, type: 3}
  m_Name: Day 2 Daughter Messages
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  personSpokenTo: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 08a894b9b170bd4408c3738b6b563b07, type: 2}
  delayBetweenMessages: 1
  lines:
  - "Hi Dad!! I hope work was good for you, sorry I can\u2019t talk properly as I\u2019ve
    been really busy working with some of the people in my accommodation."
  - "There\u2019s been a bunch of stress polluting everyone\u2019s mind about if
    their families have been ok, and supporting and helping them through it has been
    so rewarding! "
  - 'Maybe if I keep it up and the government takes notice, I might get authorization
    to be escorted outside the dome and share all of this with other likeminded people. '
  - "It\u2019s exciting, way more exciting than it should be given my situation,
    but helping others has helped me calm down just the same as I\u2019ve done for
    them."
  - Well, I hope your doing well, good luck on your next shifts and keep up the high
    effort! Your playing a great role in helping keep everyone safe.
